{"tid":544646,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁君彥向12名民主派議員發警告信  指示威行動或違法","createTime":"2018-01-29T17:14:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T00:50:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0c36c6202e7b1eb1ba1ba64c485e8dc23d28d06b","tid":544646,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T17:14:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180130/57769833\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180130%2F57769833&d=btCVXQQjrXwPBq5llfxgH04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=2b9fd86c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180130%2F57769833&h=6967d90b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180130/57769833</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會行政管理委員會主席梁君彥昨天（29日）去信12名民主派議員，指他們於上月15日立法會審議修改《議事規則》期間，與職員在立法會大樓1樓的示威行動或違反《立法會權力及特權條例》，行管會保留追究權利。<br />\n<br />\n梁於信件中指，行管會翻看閉路電視片段發現，當晚約6時半立法會進行表決時，10幾名自稱議員職員的人士試圖由1樓升降機大堂進入綠地氈（即會議廳對出）範圍示威，但被保安人員截停，有關職員及後與多名議員在大堂與綠地氈之間的範圍示威，堵塞通道，故行管會認為要向議員及相關職員發警告，指明涉嫌妨礙議員離開會議廳，或違反《立法會權力及特權條例》第382章第19(a)條。"},{"pid":"ee6148c351beb7db0f1bcbba22d6af054abec224","tid":544646,"uid":5499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T23:53:07.000Z","msg":"dq哂佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c4b05a0a4a221db7daf2e2cc638a2dde1f31b6","tid":544646,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T00:07:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69e5839a26efec0d638b10e7f152c2029b59519b","tid":544646,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T00:41:46.000Z","msg":"律政司好忙唔得閒告？"},{"pid":"a7b58df818c442e132ed11f5ce7b347853a5c2f5","tid":544646,"uid":131064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T00:5